Field Photos and Videos

Photos or videos may be provided only when they are legal, allowed, reasonable and respectful of privacy.

We do not take photos or videos in restricted, private or sensitive locations without authorization.

Reports and Information

Reports are based on available information, public observations, client-provided details and practical local checks.

A field verification report is not a legal certification, government document, audit, investigation or guarantee. It is a practical support document designed to help the client make a more informed decision.

External Costs

External costs such as transportation, paid access, shipping, third-party fees, translation, printing or professional services are not included unless agreed in advance.

